{"tid":1543481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港人權監察就831太子站觀察之回應","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:08:06.000Z","uid":29219,"like":153,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5dfdd6c8499a7f226488b552e3b55c0d168c07","tid":1543481,"uid":29219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"8月31日當晚，香港人權監察兩位觀察員到達太子站，目擊及拍攝到兩名市民被警察拘捕；當兩位觀察員靠近一名被警察制服的市民時，見到該人被警員粗暴地按壓在地上。<br />\n<br />\n兩名觀察員之後就被前來增援的防暴警察驅趕。<span style=\"color: red;\">有警員並阻止觀察員拍攝，並恫嚇觀察員，聲稱不是記者就不准拍。觀察員引述《約翰尼斯堡原則》及人權公約據理力爭，警察卻說「唔識」，接著警察用警棍驅趕觀察員到後方，並指令他們離開。</span><br />\n<br />\n當時觀察員可能因時間及位置所限，並未目擊到警察襲擊其他市民的情況。<br />\n<br />\n由於兩名觀察員不欲被迫回到地面結束在太子站的觀察，故走回車廂試圖繼續觀察，但列車竟然關門開行，把尚留在車廂的數十乘客載至石硤尾，然後才停止列車服務。當晚，位於太子站鄰近的觀察員，也再無法進入太子站。<br />\n<br />\n儘管人權監察並未觀察或拍攝到8.31襲擊事件的全貌，我們亦已向聯合國傳送了有關該事件的侵犯人權新聞報道。<br />\n<br />\n每次作出觀察，人權監察均會保留觀察員在現場所拍到的片段，以作日後供國際組織作證據。<br />\n<br />\n人權監察同時呼籲港鐵保留和公開當晚在太子站閉路電視的相關片段，以釋公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n註：人權監察會把所有當事人樣貌遮蓋後，把8.31當晚在太子站拍攝到的片段全部公開發放<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067045&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=0848baa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067045&h=254041c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067045</a>"},{"pid":"0aafa8514676d6172ffd37eb863de32220a3353f","tid":1543481,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:56:16.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7167232965636b673cd53ee1c80f6c8fa90e155","tid":1543481,"uid":29219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb0018ee010d02ce6274471432a55cfb872d7cb1","tid":1543481,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"推唔到"},{"pid":"27b71dc9bc95895c6f2cd24b6970c211c7ecf732","tid":1543481,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639923313b66e5ebb2598e4fc34ea33f2467098f","tid":1543481,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff8e9326b6d1206b8682d3457749f213ad86c08","tid":1543481,"uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"把尚留在車廂的數十乘客載至石硤尾"},{"pid":"e2137522047c60b95809dec66e814782a49cef60","tid":1543481,"uid":28111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0a93ca7a39c5fb9e6f2fe142593beadcd3274b","tid":1543481,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"P牌無力一推"},{"pid":"d43ccb3c26f6e8ad4262bd4a457468f0b52e1cb5","tid":1543481,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/u