"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"推...."},{"pid":"d3c2911349796270bad2a51951f1951571affbc8","tid":1543481,"uid":207399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79bab7eafbe8913a0ddaf794401d7f80c4d2c9e5","tid":1543481,"uid":27432,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:03:58.000Z","msg":"明晒啦咁<br />\n人權法必須要通過<br />\n9月8<br />\n美領見<br />\n麻煩放上twitter <br />\n黑警無視人權"},{"pid":"259f503da32a9d7cf1176346f54f127ce81bee57","tid":1543481,"uid":159431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"292f903f8b447861b1ef195b9a0a968bc8aaf3b4","tid":1543481,"uid":238673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"推到人權法過..."},{"pid":"c6fe0026ff04efa1669833c218105a599bb59557","tid":1543481,"uid":211578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:09:09.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n分別在於：<br />\n<br />\n殉港手足：<br />\n熊家俊先生（25歲） - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019 <br />\n何小姐（27歲） - 4/9/2019<br />\n10人離世<br />\n<br />\n還有：<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8LoZ1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8LoZ1q.jpg&h=fac47d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZTBFS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZTBFS9.jpg&h=3e1d2264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33a07855ef3fc5873278129a6614b92fc19371a8","tid":1543481,"uid":251736,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"呢件事好撚大獲， 警察正式同全世界宣戰"},{"pid":"186917349e488c93eb866c8f9b087d35730fca1b","tid":1543481,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"PISHHHHHHHHH"},{"pid":"b6154a09f203c302541fa7ae8cc2254b7e6a95e8","tid":1543481,"uid":92383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"警犬：唔識（大哂）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50880325926b6ca156209147841b2fc60d3000c0","tid":1543481,"uid":249705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下星期一 9月9 大專罷課集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為大專生<br />\n今次開學罷課搞到咁柒<br />\n完全俾中學生比下去<br />\n知道大家好慚愧 好想付出更多<br />\n<br />\n短時間內嘅主題<br />\n係要美國國會通過香港人權法案<br />\n既然7號有塞機場 8號有美國領事館<br />\n點解我哋大專生<br />\n唔襯中學生9號一週一罷<br />\n一齊搞多次罷課集會<br />\n有聲勢浩大既民意表態<br />\n既可以團聚學界<br />\n又為之後嘅三罷打強心針<br />\n<br />\n7號8號9號 一連三日嘅大型示威集會<br />\n就可以show到民意支持<br />\n俾美國國會順利表決通過條人權法<br />\n<br />\n香港就快死啦<br />\n一齊撐住好唔好<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n洗版洗到有組織搞9月9罷課為止</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1ce01c601e7552627761a7dd003e890cd53d7a4","tid":1543481,"uid":60563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0f8f4ca91539a144e77328e633110e